snippet.textDisplay: Old Town Road is the most monotonic, moronic and just downright stupid song, ever. Lil Nas X knows sweet fuck all about being a cowboy. It's about as deep as Cotton-Eyed Joe, but the clunky hip-hop beat means it doesn't work as a novelty party song, and all the oh-so culturally on-point wokeness takes any fun out of it. The real reason it's such a big hit is because any fool with a five-note range can sing it, and its simplicity makes it accessible worldwide (they love it where I'm living in Cambodia and Laos right now). But hey, I guess it's better than listening to Cardi fucking B.
snippet.textOriginal: Old Town Road is the most monotonic, moronic and just downright stupid song, ever. Lil Nas X knows sweet fuck all about being a cowboy.
